<P>
What so many anti-gun fanatics fail to realize is why the 2nd Amendment was 
added to the Constitution. It was not added so that citizens could own weapons 
for hunting, target shooting, collecting or even for protecting their lives, 
their families or their property from criminals. It was added for one reason: 
so that the people could protect themselves from the government. 
</P>
