</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
LAS VEGAS SUN (NEWSPAPER); LAS VEGAS REVIEW JOURNAL (NEWSPAPER); NEWSPAPERS -- 
NEVADA; LAS VEGAS (NV); MERGERS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
