<TEXT>
<P>
Though it may not rank with "Miami Vice" or "In the Heat of the Night," I find 
"Hunter" to be a well-written, well-acted and fast-moving series. Fred Dryer is 
excellent, as is Stepfanie Kramer. 
</P>
<P>
Gary Traxler, North Hollywood 
</P>
