<HEADLINE>
<P>
CONFIDENCE DECLINES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
About 34% of Americans believe that real estate brokers hae low ethical 
standards, up six percentage points from the 1983 1983 Gallup poll, according 
to the September issue of Money magazine. 
</P>
